- **`parallelStream()`** splits the work across all available CPU cores automatically
- **`ThreadLocal<XPath>`** ensures no thread contention — each thread reuses its own `XPath` instance without creating a new one per record
- **`toConcurrentMap()`** handles concurrent writes to the result map safely
